# Linting

- **Config:** ESLint in `eslint.config.mjs`. Run `npm run lint`; `eslint --fix` auto-fixes.
- **Pre-commit:** Husky runs lint-staged on staged `.js`, `.mjs`, `.cjs`, `.ts`, `.tsx`; failed lint aborts commit.
- **Rule:** Do not introduce new lint errors; fix or suppress only with explicit justification.
